dct_title_s: Vepriai / Vyr[iausiojo] štabo karo topogr[afijos] skyrius.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contour intervals and spot heights. After converting the horizontal numbers to meters in 2 steps (4.2672 meter), the numbers are rounded up to whole numbers Upper right margin: "419". [Vyr[iausiojo] štabo karo topogr[afijos] skyrius = Department of Military Topography of the General Staff].
